                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8429" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2117</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1474 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生态似水，转型如舟-青化民爆的绿色转型之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ecology is like water, transformation is like a boat - the green transformation journey of Qinghua and the people under the concept of ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梁运吉，冯欣茹，刘妍，许春蕾，陈博轩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑龙江青化民爆器材有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色转型；ESG理念；民爆企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green transition;ESG concept; Civil explosive enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国家“十四五”规划提出“碳达峰”和“碳中和”这一绿色目标，以可持续发展为代表的绿色理念越来越受到社会各界的欢迎和重视。党的二十大报告指出“加快构建新发展格局，着力推动高质量发展”。高质量是国内经济发展步入新时代的主旋律，也是各行业企业未来发展的突破方向。而企业高质量发展的本质特征就是进行绿色转型发展，强调节能环保，实现绿色增长。与传统意义上只涉及经济发展的单一理念不同，它更注重经济、社会和生态等各方面的协调，致力于实现经济与社会的双赢。基于此，以环境、社会和公司治理为核心的ESG理念，快速在全球范围内崛起。为顺应企业发展的需要与国家在节能减排方面的高要求，本案例中的青化民爆器材有限公司以ESG理念为引领，以全面绿色转型为抓手，坚定不移的走生态优先的绿色转型道路。本案例旨在通过理论与实践的融合，利用波特假说、高阶梯队理论对企业绿色转型动因进行分析，同时，引导学生对青化民爆的绿色转型历程进行深入思考，帮助学生深入了解企业如何进行绿色转型。通过分析企业在绿色转型进程中可能存在的机会与风险，据此来进行企业绿色转型的路径选择，同时为青化民爆未来的深层次绿色转型寻找新的方向。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The national &quot;14th Five-Year Plan&quot; puts forward the green goals of &quot;carbon peak&quot; and &quot;carbon neutrality&quot;, and the green concept represented by sustainable development has been increasingly welcomed and valued by all sectors of society. The report of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China pointed out that &quot;accelerate the construction of a new development pattern and strive to promote high-quality development&quot;. High quality is the main theme of domestic economic development in a new era, and it is also the breakthrough direction of the future development of enterprises in various industries. The essential feature of high-quality development of enterprises is to carry out green transformation and development, emphasize energy conservation and environmental protection, and achieve green growth. Different from the traditional concept that only involves economic development, it pays more attention to the coordination of economic, social and ecological aspects, and is committed to achieving a win-win situation for the economy and society. Based on this, the ESG concept with environmental, social and corporate governance as the core has rapidly risen on a global scale. In order to meet the needs of enterprise development and the country&#39;s high requirements for energy conservation and emission reduction, Qinghua Civil Explosive Equipment Co., Ltd. in this case is guided by the ESG concept, takes comprehensive green transformation as the starting point, and unswervingly takes the green transformation path of ecological priority. Through the integration of theory and practice, this case aims to analyze the motivation of green transformation of enterprises by using Porter&#39;s hypothesis and high-echelon theory, and at the same time, guide students to think deeply about the green transformation process of Qinghua Minbang, and help students have an in-depth understanding of how enterprises carry out green transformation. By analyzing the possible opportunities and risks of enterprises in the process of green transformation, we can choose the path of green transformation of enterprises accordingly, and at the same time find a new direction for the in-depth green transformation of Qinghua Minbang in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色转型理论；波特假说理论；高阶梯队理论；绿色转型成效；绿色供应链理论；ESG与企业价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-07</td>
                            </tr>
